# Docker build context trimming for crates/tesseract-ocr-web/Dockerfile.
# Keep: crates/ source, Cargo.toml, corpus/model (bundled at runtime).
# (Cargo.lock is gitignored repo-wide, so the build resolves deps fresh — pin
# LANCE_GRAPH_REF / NDARRAY_REF for reproducibility.)
# Drop everything heavy or build-irrelevant so the context upload stays small.

# Build residue (the single biggest item — can be many GB).
target/
**/target/

# VCS + CI + editor.
.git/
.github/
.gitignore
.vscode/
.idea/

# Agent/session material and harvested oracles — not needed to build the binary.
.claude/

# Corpus: only corpus/model is needed (copied into the runtime image). Drop the
# rest (test pages, golden / hiertext fixtures) so a local `docker build` does
# not upload them.
corpus/*
!corpus/model

# Docs.
*.md
**/*.md

# Local env / secrets — never ship these into a build context.
.env
*.env
